Secondly, The Princes Prerogative, whoſe Office is to protect and puniſh, to defend the innocent, and correct the Spirit of Contumacy and Rebellion, relieve the oppreſſed, and ſupport the vertuous;

 rewards to Merit, as well as puniſhment to Sin and Vice are diſpenſed: A terrour to evil doers,
                  1 Pet. 2.14. (ſaith the Text) and praiſe to them that do well. Therefore honour the King.
